entry.value: SELECT FF.rowprocessed, FF.datasetName, FF.filedate, FF.filename, FF.sourceid, ${now():format('yyyyMMdd')} as dateload FROM ( SELECT datasetName, filedate, filename, sourceid, count(*) - 1 as rowprocessed FROM FLOWFILE WHERE sourceid <> 'sourceid' GROUP BY datasetName, filedate , filename, sourceid ) FF
